{"tid":2077243,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（月經）非在學人士想改善英文能力討論","createTime":"2020-06-24T06:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T13:28:36.000Z","uid":3539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"323527905400f6fbf2f59d3d7799e27fc7c61d7a","tid":2077243,"uid":3539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:46:59.000Z","msg":"明明自己寫英文就可以好快好流暢 同埋寫到啲見得人既英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但偏偏講就好似詞不達意 好似要用個腦寫左一句野 再用個口講出黎咁 但次次想講既時候 個腦停頓左咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點樣可以改善呢個問題 （因為想考ielts睇下有無移民機會 但咁搞法怕連6分都拎唔到）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我有keep住聽podcast再跟入面既人物講番句野出黎<br />\n跟住佢講就無問題 但當同人用英文交談時 講野甩甩咳咳 好似詞不達意 想講果句又講唔到出黎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家覺得可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89503a22f39ebed224090266b26f4f36db60a692","tid":2077243,"uid":358604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:56:01.000Z","msg":"睇我學英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ee24b41b581838b41ff4feb77269e0b1e4d13f","tid":2077243,"uid":3539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89503a22f39ebed224090266b26f4f36db60a692","tid":2077243,"uid":358604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:56:01.000Z","msg":"睇我學英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:03:36.000Z","msg":"你？不了<br />\n我以前都會睇毛ee"},{"pid":"9b764219f6102799f72bea173c4937438d346b5e","tid":2077243,"uid":6589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:24:08.000Z","msg":"打機同人傾計<br />\n<br />\n有隻game以